# AIPS — absolute isopropyl alcohol (GOST grade) for coatings and cleaning

{% callout title="Brief" %}
High-purity absolute isopropyl alcohol according to GOST. Used as a diluent for alcohol-based foundry coatings and as a universal cleaner and degreaser for moulds and equipment. 
