- Do not mix with strong oxidising agents or active chlorine sources.

## Packaging, storage and safety

AIPS is supplied in sealed containers suitable for flammable liquids (drums, cans, etc.). Store in a cool, well-ventilated place away from heat and ignition sources, in accordance with GOST 9805-84 and fire safety regulations. 
